    "valueProposition": "A Tier II (Velocity) compliance solution, priced at $500-2000/month, immediately delivers a clear ROI by eliminating significant operational inefficiencies and mitigating catastrophic risks. By automating manual processes, it frees up critical validation team time, conservatively saving a medium-sized company at least $175,000 annually. This means the solution pays for itself in approximately 31 days just on time savings alone. Factoring in the avoidance of even a minor audit finding or consultant engagement, the ROI can rapidly escalate to 10x or more annually. This isn't just cost avoidance; it's an investment in operational resilience, market speed, and brand integrity, transforming compliance from an overhead into a measurable business asset."
